  Locus:
    Page: 131
    Verse: 11
Tags:
  - Enthusiasm
---
The Greeks have given us one of the most beautiful words of our language,
the word “enthusiasm” -- a god within. The grandeur of the acts of men
is measured by the inspiration from which they spring. Happy is he who bears
a God within.
